p:
Chemical composition. Essential oil (main components are alkanes, such as 6,10,14-trimethyl-2-pentadecanone and tricosane, besides linalool, E-anethole) (
 Fitsiou et al., 2007; 
 Kowalski et al., 2017); flavonoids (e.g., quercetin, kaempferol, and derivatives; tiliroside), anthocyanins (
 Negri et al., 2013; 
 Fawzy et al., 2018).
